riker endlich gemeinsam um ein differenziertes Bild. Dieser Sammelband diskutiert die Ursachen und Wirkungen des italienischen Intervento von 1915 in neuer Sicht und leistet damit einen Beitrag zum wissenschaftlichen Dialog zwischen den ehemaligen Kriegsgegnern, der noch längst nicht beendet ist.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a FA license: uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/free-access-policy uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aWorld War, 1914-1918zItaly. 4aDeutschland. 4aErster Weltkrieg. 4aItalien. 4aMilitärgeschichte. 4aÖsterreich. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aAfflerbach, Holger, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCalì, Vincenzo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHürter, Johannes, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLabanca, Nicola, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRusconi, Gian Enrico, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRusconi, Gian Enrico, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aÜberegger, Oswald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978348658278940uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/9783486706291zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486706291zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486706291/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-OGSc2005d2012